reviewText: WW 11 BUFF THIS ADDS TO MY COLLECTION
Early release in the States by the young American International Pictures. It's refreshing to see a patriotic English military picture.
A very good film of the time . It may be best that it did not show the true murderous actions of the CT forces .
not bad pic qu for a old movie This movie has a docu-drama feel in places and employs a lot of stock footage. 16mm.
